#. <section class="sutta" id="an10.40"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.40:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.40:0.2"
msgid "4. Upālivagga"
msgstr "4. With Upāli"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.40:0.3"
msgid "40. Dutiyaānandasutta"
msgstr "40. With Ānanda (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an10.40:1.1"
msgid "“‘Saṅghasāmaggī, saṅghasāmaggī’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of ‘harmony in the Saṅgha’."

msgctxt "an10.40:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, saṅgho samaggo hotī”ti?"
msgstr "How is harmony in the Saṅgha defined?”"

msgctxt "an10.40:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Idhānanda, bhikkhū adhammaṃ adhammoti dīpenti, dhammaṃ dhammoti dīpenti, "
"avinayaṃ avinayoti dīpenti, vinayaṃ vinayoti dīpenti, abhāsitaṃ alapitaṃ "
"tathāgatena abhāsitaṃ alapitaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti, bhāsitaṃ lapitaṃ "
"tathāgatena bhāsitaṃ lapitaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti, anāciṇṇaṃ tathāgatena "
"anāciṇṇaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti, āciṇṇaṃ tathāgatena āciṇṇaṃ tathāgatenāti "
"dīpenti, apaññattaṃ tathāgatena apaññattaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti, paññattaṃ "
"tathāgatena paññattaṃ tathāgatenāti dīpenti."
msgstr ""
"“Ānanda, it’s when a mendicant explains what is not the teaching as not the "
"teaching, and what is the teaching as the teaching. They explain what is not "
"the training as not the training, and what is the training as the training. "
"They explain what was not spoken and stated by the Realized One as not "
"spoken and stated by the Realized One, and what was spoken and stated by the "
"Realized One as spoken and stated by the Realized One. They explain what was "
"not practiced by the Realized One as not practiced by the Realized One, and "
"what was practiced by the Realized One as practiced by the Realized One. "
"They explain what was not prescribed by the Realized One as not prescribed "
"by the Realized One, and what was prescribed by the Realized One as "
"prescribed by the Realized One."

msgctxt "an10.40:1.4"
msgid ""
"Te imehi dasahi vatthūhi na avakassanti na apakassanti na āveni kammāni "
"karonti na āveni pātimokkhaṃ uddisanti."
msgstr ""
"On these ten grounds they don’t split off and go their own way. They don’t "
"perform legal acts autonomously or recite the monastic code autonomously."

msgctxt "an10.40:1.5"
msgid "Ettāvatā kho, ānanda, saṅgho samaggo hotī”ti."
msgstr "That is how harmony in the Saṅgha is defined.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an10.40:2.1"
msgid "“Bhinnaṃ pana, bhante, saṅghaṃ samaggaṃ katvā kiṃ so pasavatī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But sir, what does someone who has created harmony in a schismatic Saṅgha "
"bring upon themselves?”"

msgctxt "an10.40:2.2"
msgid "“Brahmaṃ, ānanda, puññaṃ pasavatī”ti."
msgstr "“They bring divine merit upon themselves.”"

msgctxt "an10.40:2.3"
msgid "“Kiṃ pana, bhante, brahmaṃ puññan”ti?"
msgstr "“But what is divine merit?”"

msgctxt "an10.40:2.4"
msgid "“Kappaṃ, ānanda, saggamhi modatīti—"
msgstr "“They rejoice in heaven for an eon, Ānanda."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.77"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.1"
msgid "Sukhā saṃghassa sāmaggī,"
msgstr "A Saṅgha in harmony is happy,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.2"
msgid "samaggānañca anuggaho;"
msgstr "as is support for those in harmony."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.3"
msgid "Samaggarato dhammaṭṭho,"
msgstr "Basing themselves in the teaching,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.4"
msgid "yogakkhemā na dhaṃsati;"
msgstr "favoring harmony, they destroy no sanctuary."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.5"
msgid "Saṃghaṃ samaggaṃ katvāna,"
msgstr "After creating harmony in the Saṅgha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:3.6"
msgid "kappaṃ saggamhi modatī”ti."
msgstr "they rejoice in heaven for an eon.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.40:3.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.40:3.8"
msgid "Upālivaggo catuttho."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an10.40:4.1"
msgid "Upāli ṭhapanā ubbāho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:4.2"
msgid "upasampadanissayā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:4.3"
msgid "Sāmaṇero ca dve bhedā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an10.40:4.4"
msgid "ānandehi pare duveti."
msgstr ""
